title: 'Scuba-diving' lizard can stay underwater for 16 minutes

title_detail.value: 'Scuba-diving' lizard can stay underwater for 16 minutes

summary: A Costa Rican lizard species may have evolved scuba-diving qualities allowing it to stay underwater for 16 minutes, according to researchers.
